<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>Rewards Dashboard</title>

  <style>
    :root {
      --bg: #f3f5fb;
      --card: #ffffff;
      --text: #0f172a;
      --muted: #6b7280;
      --border: #e5e7eb;
      --accent: #4f46e5;
    }

    * {
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background: var(--bg);
      color: var(--text);
    }

    .container {
      max-width: 1050px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 45px 18px;
    }

    header {
      margin-bottom: 35px;
    }

    header h1 {
      font-size: 32px;
      font-weight: 800;
      margin: 0;
      letter-spacing: -0.5px;
    }

    header p {
      margin: 8px 0 0;
      font-size: 15px;
      color: var(--muted);
    }

    .grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(340px, 1fr));
      gap: 22px;
    }

    .card {
      background: var(--card);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 18px;
      padding: 24px;
      box-shadow: 0 3px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
    }

    .badge {
      display: inline-block;
      background: rgba(79,70,229,0.12);
      color: var(--accent);
      padding: 6px 12px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      font-size: 12px;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }

    .card h2 {
      font-size: 22px;
      font-weight: 800;
      margin: 0 0 12px;
    }

    .card p {
      font-size: 15px;
      line-height: 1.7;
      margin: 10px 0;
      color: var(--text);
    }

    .divider {
      height: 1px;
      background: var(--border);
      margin: 18px 0;
    }

    .section-title {
      font-size: 16px;
      font-weight: 800;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }

    .list b {
      font-weight: 800;
      display: inline-block;
      margin-top: 12px;
    }

  </style>
</head>

<body>

  <div class="container">

    <header>
      <h1>Rewards Dashboard</h1>
      <p>Participation tracking and reward distribution system</p>
    </header>

    <div class="grid">

      <!-- MONTHLY RAFFLE -->
      <div class="card">

        <div class="badge">MONTHLY PROGRAM</div>
        <h2>🎁 Monthly Raffle</h2>

        <p>
          Any child with <b>90% participation</b> will be entered into our monthly raffle.
          Winners are selected on the <b>last day of every month</b>.
        </p>

        <div class="divider"></div>

        <div class="section-title">🏆 February Winners</div>

        <p class="list">

          <b>$10 Gift Cards:</b><br>
          Ava S. • Liam K. • Noah R. • Emma T. • Sophia B.<br><br>

          <b>$50 Gift Cards:</b><br>
          Chaim A. • Jordan B. • Madison C.<br><br>

          <b>Board Games:</b><br>
          Sima A. • Noah B. • Ava C.<br><br>

          <b>LEGO Sets:</b><br>
          Ethan A. • Sophia B. • Benjamin C.<br><br>

          <b>Tickets:</b><br>
          Chava A. • Mason B. • Emily C.

        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- PARTICIPATION REWARDS -->
      <div class="card">

        <div class="badge">INCENTIVE PROGRAM</div>
        <h2>🎉 Participation Rewards</h2>

        <p>
          Keep up the good work, kids — to date, we’ve given away <b>thousands of dollars</b> in rewards.
        </p>

        <p>
          Anyone who has just started following their guidelines may ask their Hospital of CARE provider
          to apply for the <b>$50 beginner’s bonus</b>.
        </p>

        <p>
          Please ensure that all paperwork is submitted in a <b>timely manner</b>.
        </p>

      </div>

    </div>

  </div>

</body>
</html>
